commentaries.text:
14. The dead shall not live. {Bogus footnote}

<vq>The slain shall not rise again.</vq> {Bogus footnote}

<vq>Therefore hast thou visited and destroyed them.</vq> This is added for the sake of explanation; for it assigns the reason why the reprobate perish without hope, namely, because it is the purpose of God to destroy them. In the wrath of God they have nothing to look for but death and ruin.
